==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mattoir
<hw>Mat*toir"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>matoir</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Engraving)</fld> <def>A kind of coarse
punch with a rasplike face, used for making a rough surface on etching
ground, or on the naked copper, the effect after biting being very
similar to stippled lines.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mattowacca</ent>⟦br⟧
